name: Waves
description:
Inspired by 80s synthwave vibe, I recorded this track using Korg analog synth and Novation Bass Station 2 synth and some drum samples. All the patches was designed by me and tuned to A=432hz for a different experience.
For the cover did some basic coding on hydra. This is the second of 5 tracks i'll release soon exclusive as NFT.

This is the third piece of my EP "pixelate" 3/5.
It called "Waves". Recorded in A=432hz

Gear for this track
Korg Minilogue - synth
Novation Bass Station 2 - synth
SSL2+ - audiobox
Ableton Live 11
